There is almost nothing to the FFI interface: Basically, the asm FFI can only have asm types, as you would expect. Then you can just call normal JS methods that were imported. So stuff like<p><pre><code>    function asmFunc(import) {
      &#x27;use asm&#x27;;

      var externFunc = import.externFunc;

      function asmFunc() {
        externFunc(123, -0.5);
      }

      return asmFunc;
    }
</code></pre>
What extra info are you looking for?
